item.title: Not eating
item.dc:creator: @Tom Tom
item.description:
@Tom wrote:

I think you should eat something, whever you want to or not. Not eating is going to make you ill. Woman get like this during pregnancy, I believe it is also found most commonly in woman. It can be signs off a serious health problem. Some things I found on the net,

[ul][li]Depression - this can cause the ‘I don’t want to eat’ feeling.[/li][/ul]

[ul][li]Physically inactive - You need to exercise more.[/li][/ul]

[ul][li]Unbalanced Diet - become nourished. By having a balanced diet.[/li][/ul]

Also, try eating something you feel comfortable with, this maybe a orange? An apple? Anything a start.
